          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "气盖天地，忠感鬼神，哪怕它龙潭虎穴，岂能怯而不往。是我一路行来，餐风"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "露宿，十分劳乏，眼前荆州不远，趁着天气清和，就此马上加鞭！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "催坐骑我直奔荆州驿站，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
