    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "中军",
        "刘表",
        "祢衡",
        "蔡夫人"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军、刘表同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荆襄八郡地，文武一身尊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某，荆州牧刘表。昨日曹丞相有书到来，将祢衡推荐与我。我想祢衡乃天下知"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "名之士，那曹孟德平日礼贤下士，何以弃而不用，推荐前来？其中必有缘故。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不免将夫人请出，再作计较！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军，有请夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请夫人！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军下。蔡夫人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听主公唤，移步到堂前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡夫人进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妾身有礼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人少礼。请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。主公，将妾身唤出，有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人，是你不知，昨日接到曹丞相一信，荐来祢衡。那祢正平乃天下知名之士，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹孟德何以弃而不用，推荐前来与我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也太糊涂了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我怎么糊涂呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听妾道来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那祢衡生来禀性狂，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怎能够与曹操共处一堂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因此上才将他转荐外方。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这便是借你刀来把他伤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那曹操他对人假模假样"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若是主公你不加容量"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。曹操他杀了祢衡，怕天下人耻笑，难道我就不怕么！夫人，你看此"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事如何处置才好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若依妾身作主张，"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不如荐他到外厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荐到哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江夏黄祖，生性鲁莽，且将他荐到那里，再看如何。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫人高见，正合孤意。夫人请回，我就依计而行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蔡夫人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蔡夫人下。中军上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀主公：祢衡求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐升帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "升帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡进见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡进见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内西皮导板） 听中军传一声命我进见，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘景升果然是不能尊贤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "且把那国家事讲在当前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡进见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公在上，祢衡拜见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少礼。请坐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正平，你由朝中到来，朝中之事如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那曹瞒在朝中大权独揽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "眼见得汉家业被他推翻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕只怕荆州地也难苟安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "公本是天潢派岂可不管"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公本是天潢派岂可不管"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那祢衡当孤面对我责难，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "生就了狂妄性名不虚传。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我把你荐黄祖这有何难。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "公本是天潢派岂可不管"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正平，孤家这里，地僻事少，不足以容高贤之驾。意欲将你荐于黄祖帐下，你"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可愿去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若是杀了他曹操笑俺"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倘若是杀了他曹操笑俺"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "那曹贼定下了借刀之计，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "刘景升虽庸暗岂能不知？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "也不过转借刀将我命追。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "破出去一身死有何稀奇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘若是杀了他曹操笑俺"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明公既然荐俺，岂有不去之理。就此告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他将我荐黄祖哪有好意"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我若是不敢去惹他耻笑"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别了刘景升忙跨坐骑，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡上马。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我见了那黄祖再看高低。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘表",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只见那祢正平扬长去了，"
        }
      ],
