          "text": "（四下手、黄祖同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "威震东江，统貔貅，谁人敢当！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼生来性鲁莽，带领甲兵逞刚强。哪怕东吴兵将广，谅他不敢窥边墙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫、大将黄祖。奉了主公之命，镇守江夏，今日升帐，不知有何军情来报！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启爷：主公有令，命祢衡来见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我闻祢衡乃天下有名之士，今日远来，好幸会也！有请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我迎接。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请祢先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。祢衡上，黄祖出迎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢先生，你来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡 （同笑） 啊哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄祖、祢衡同进，同揖坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生远路驾临，未去远迎，多多得罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好说。岂敢劳动将军！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，老夫久闻大名，今日相见，其乃幸会也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中军，安排酒宴伺侯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（中军摆酒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生请酒！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吹牌子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢先生，我闻先生从曹丞相处转荐而来！曹丞相部下，有些什么人才，讲来一"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹营中俱都是无能之辈，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "惟杨修与孔融人才出奇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "比到我也只算大儿小儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他二人虽然是天下名士"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "比老夫如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "论到了老将军本无可此，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺祢衡说实话恕不恭维。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "虽然是受香烟却少灵机！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄祖怒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好匹夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "进帐来老夫我款待于你，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你竟敢筵席前把我来欺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一霎时我定把他首级来提！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡大笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺祢衡自生来无忧无惧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我把那千年事看作须臾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "未来时早也就料定于你"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你料我什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我料你这盗跖难容仲尼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个祢衡，越发无礼！你藐视世人，全不如你，你把你的本领说来我听！如果"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "近乎情理，我便饶你不死！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡冷笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿嘿嘿……你且听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "祢衡生来志气豪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "读诗书明礼义道德崇高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曾学三略与六韬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上欺天子下压群僚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "才借击鼓骂曹操。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "彩凤焉能住鹊巢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哪有好言对尔曹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "诸子百家我尽晓"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都只为佞臣出专权当道"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我有心替我主把奸贼扫"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "前去荆州见刘表"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我今到此大数到"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃大言不惭！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我好比在天仁义鸟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "贼好比食母野鸱枭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "贼好比野火遍地烧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我好比雷鸣天下晓"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你便有天大本领，人家不用，也是枉然！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我不戴乱臣乌纱帽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我不穿贼子的蟒龙袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "落一个青史美名标。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我只要能为忠和孝"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就不怕死么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "常言道三寸气在千般好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一旦无常万事抛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡狂笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫黄祖休迟疑请你开刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好个大胆祢正平，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说出话来理不通。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "识时务者为英雄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不如把你问斩刑！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此人一味倔强，终非有为之士，斩就斩了罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军校们，推出斩首！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "明哲保身有古训"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "留你这狂生有何用"
        },
        {
          "character": "四下手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二下手押祢衡同下。黄射上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说要斩祢先生，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "后帐来了讲情人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父亲面前说分明！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见父亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迈步且把大帐进"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿不在后帐，到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿在后帐，闻听父亲要斩祢衡！想那祢衡乃天下知名之士，曹丞相、刘主公"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄射",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尚且容他，父亲如要将他斩了，岂不被天下人笑骂！"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄祖",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿讲得有理。快快传令，将祢先生放回！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
